5A334C6A.Line1.7FA05: Good news for once, I hope?

5B80055C.Line21.7FA05: It’s written in our code. He sent a plan—though calling it that is generous. He wants to imprison Lilith with my soulstone—the one that held Astaroth.

7BAACD41.Line35.7FA05: Go to the Horadric Vault, will you? I’ll dig up what he needs. You can deliver it, and maybe then he’ll leave me alone.

C351EB64.Line29.7FA05: Certainly not! The stone needs to be attuned first. And he will need an expert for that.

D7101683.Line19.7FA05: He didn’t tell you? No. Of course not. That would require some basic degree of consideration.

E1B653BF.Line33.7FA05: Then he is even more foolish than I thought.

FA823896.Line31.BAE4: Lorath thinks that expert is you.

FB3FFC35.MenuLabel: “I have a letter for you, Donan.”
